ğŸ”¹ Why we used React.js in frontend?
â€œWe chose React.js for the frontend because it helps us build a fast and dynamic Single Page Application. React allows component reusability, smooth navigation without page reloads, and easy integration with backend APIs. Since our backend is also JavaScript (Node.js), development and integration became simpler. So React helped us create a scalable and maintainable UI.â€

