âœ… Interview One-Line Answer

â€œApart from online self-booking, we also support booking through phone calls. The receptionist enters visitor details during the call, our backend checks slot availability, stores the booking in MongoDB, and automatically sends WhatsApp confirmations to both host and visitor.â€

